322
00:45:25,663 --> 00:45:26,847
Pipa!

323
00:45:27,830 --> 00:45:28,954
Pipa!

324
00:45:29,041 --> 00:45:30,089
Pipa!

325
00:45:30,177 --> 00:45:31,253
Pipa!

326
